<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title}}</title>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen relative">
<header class="flex flex-col relative overflow-clip h-screen">
    <picture class="absolute inset-0">
        <source srcset="{{htmlWebpackPlugin.files.publicPath}}media/Bitmama-Reply-Wallpaper_2100p_b.jpg" media="(min-width: 2100px)">
        <source srcset="{{htmlWebpackPlugin.files.publicPath}}media/Bitmama-Reply-Wallpaper_1200p_b.jpg" media="(min-width: 1200px)">
        <img src="{{htmlWebpackPlugin.files.publicPath}}media/Bitmama-Reply-Wallpaper_1080p_b.jpg" alt="" class="h-full w-full object-cover object-bottom">
    </picture>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col px-16 text-white">
        {{> aria-menubar headerContent="head-content" mainContent="main-content"}}
        <aside class="border border-white w-fit p-2 rounded-md self-end">
            <dl class="list__wrapper list__wrapper--vertical text-xs">
                <dt class="list__title mt-2 ">Risorse</dt>
                <dd class="mr-4 underline"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/templates/components/aria-menubar_component.html">Codice html del widget menubar</a></dd>
                <dd class="underline"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/js/shadow/menu_bar.js">Codice javascript del widget menubar</a></dd>
            </dl>
        </aside>
        <div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto grow flex flex-col justify-center">
            <section
                    id="head-content"
                    class="max-w-screen-sm mb-32">
                <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold mb-8">Aria</h1>
                <p class="mb-2">Con <em>Accessible Rich Internet Applications</em> si intendono un insieme di ruoli e
                    attributi che definiscono meccanismi per rendere contenuti web e applicazioni web più accessibili a
                    utenti con disabilità</p>
                <p class="mb-4">La prima regola dell'uso degli ARIA è che se esiste un componente nativamente supportato
                    dai browser è preferibile a qualsiasi implementazione personalizzata, le altre si potrebbero riassumere con <em>Nessun aria è meglio di cattivi aria</em>. Vediamo alcuni esempi di implementazione della select nativa qui sotto:</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <label for="native-aria">Quali ARIA sono meglio?</label>
                        <select id="native-aria" name="native-aria" class="p-4 rounded-md text-black">
                            <option value="" selected>Seleziona un'opzione</option>
                            <option value="no">Nessun Aria</option>
                            <option value="bad">Cattivi Aria</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
<main class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto p-16 flex-grow w-full z-[3]" id="main-content">
    <section class="flex flex-col w-full mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-4">Custom select</h2>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Widget semanticamente sbagliato ma interattivo</h3>
        <div class="list-box__wrapper mt-4 bg-red-200 p-4 rounded-md mb-8" id="bad-aria" is="bad-box">
            <label id="bad-type">Which aria is better?</label>
            <div class="list-box__button"></div>
            <ul class="list-box__container" tabindex="-1">
                <li class="list-box__option">
                    Select option
                </li>
                <li class="list-box__option">
                    No aria
                </li>
                <li class="list-box__option">
                    Bad aria
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Widget semanticamente corretto ma non interattivo</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-col mt-4 bg-red-200 p-4 rounded-md mb-8">
            <p id="list-aria">Which aria is better?</p>
            <ul role="listbox" aria-labelledby="list-aria">
                <li role="option" aria-selected="true">select option</li>
                <li role="option" aria-selected="false">no aria</li>
                <li role="option" aria-selected="false">bad aria</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Widget completo</h3>
        {{> aria-combobox}}
        <dl class="list__wrapper list__wrapper--horizontal">
            <dt class="list__title mt-2 ">Risorse</dt>
            <dd class="mr-4 underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/templates/components/aria-combobox_component.html">Codice html del widget combobox</a></dd>
            <dd class="underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/js/shadow/listBox.js">Codice javascript del widget combobox</a></dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
    <section class="flex flex-col w-full px-2">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-4">Other widgets</h2>
        <section class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Radio and checkboxes</h3>
            {{> aria-radiogroup}}
            {{> aria-checkbox}}
            <dl class="list__wrapper list__wrapper--horizontal">
                <dt class="list__title mt-2 ">Risorse</dt>
                <dd class="mr-4 underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/templates/components/aria-radiogroup_component.html">Codice html del widget radiogroup</a></dd>
                <dd class="mr-4 underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/js/shadow/radiogroup.js">Codice javascript del widget radiogroup</a></dd>
                <dd class="mr-4 underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/templates/components/aria-checkbox_component.html">Codice html del widget checkbox</a></dd>
                <dd class="underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/js/shadow/checkbox.js">Codice javascript del widget checkbox</a></dd>
            </dl>
        </section>
        <section class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Carousel</h3>
            {{> aria-carousel}}
            <dl class="list__wrapper list__wrapper--horizontal">
                <dt class="list__title mt-2 ">Risorse</dt>
                <dd class="mr-4 underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/templates/components/aria-carousel_component.html">Codice html del widget carousel</a></dd>
                <dd class="underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/js/shadow/carousel.js">Codice javascript del widget carousel</a></dd>
            </dl>
        </section>
        <section class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Tabber</h3>
            {{> aria-tabber}}
            <dl class="list__wrapper list__wrapper--horizontal">
                <dt class="list__title mt-2 ">Risorse</dt>
                <dd class="mr-4 underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/templates/components/aria-tabber_component.html">Codice html del widget tabber</a></dd>
                <dd class="underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/js/shadow/tablist.js">Codice javascript del widget tabber</a></dd>
            </dl>
        </section>
        <section class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold    mb-4">Live regions</h3>
            {{> aria-liveRegion}}
            <dl class="list__wrapper list__wrapper--horizontal">
                <dt class="list__title mt-2 ">Risorse</dt>
                <dd class="mr-4 underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/templates/components/aria-liveRegion_component.html">Codice html dell'esempio di live region</a></dd>
                <dd class="underline text-blue-600"><a href="https://github.com/agreaste/prometeo/blob/master/src/js/pages/aria.js#L93">Codice javascript dell'esempio di live region</a></dd>
            </dl>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Casi particolari</h3>
            <p>Alcuni elementi, come span o div, per molti lettori di schermo, non avendo nessun significato semantico, non reggono l'attributo aria-label: <span aria-label="Altro contenuto di questo span">Il contenuto di questo span</span></p>
        </section>
    </section>
</main>
{{> footer}}
</body>
</html>